  // improved by: Brett Zamir (http://brett-zamir.me)
  // improved by: Theriault
  // improved by: Kevin van Zonneveld (http://kevin.vanzonneveld.net)
  // bugfixed by: Michael White (http://getsprink.com)
  // bugfixed by: Benjamin Lupton
